name: Zuharu
description: Zuharu is a 2D artist who makes pinups/art of characters from video games and animes such as Spy x Family, Mushoku Tensei, Dungeon ni Deai, Kill la Kill and several others. They attempt to mimic the art of the source material as closely as possible.​​​​
